=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains details about the storage configuration of the knowledge base
in MongoDB Atlas.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> CollectionName => Str

The collection name of the knowledge base in MongoDB Atlas.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> CredentialsSecretArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the secret that you created in
Secrets Manager that contains user credentials for your MongoDB Atlas
cluster.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> DatabaseName => Str

The database name in your MongoDB Atlas cluster for your knowledge
base.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Endpoint => Str

The endpoint URL of your MongoDB Atlas cluster for your knowledge base.


=head2 EndpointServiceName => Str

The name of the VPC endpoint service in your account that is connected
to your MongoDB Atlas cluster.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> FieldMapping => L<Paws::BedrockAgent::MongoDbAtlasFieldMapping>

Contains the names of the fields to which to map information about the
vector store.


=head2 TextIndexName => Str

The name of the text search index in the MongoDB collection. This is
required for using the hybrid search feature.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> VectorIndexName => Str

The name of the MongoDB Atlas vector search index.



